overview: PowerFortunes.com is run by a group of accomplished experts from the fields of astrology, the tarot and fortune telling and astrological products, backed by a professional support crew bringing you the unique experience of benefiting from ancient knowledge and beliefs through a modern day way of functioning, you would expect of any professional service. This Site has undergone substantial content changes and additions since it first went online in 2003. Products & Services This Site offers many unique astrological products and services, including unique amulets and energised talismans. There are also several quality free services such as, a free online fortune telling service, free monthly horoscopes and a free MP3 affirmation download facility. Careful attention is paid to each astrology / tarot reading, astrology compatibility report, request for information and order for products. The staff and management at PowerFortunes.com use the same products that they send out to their customers, which they guarantee are authentic in nature. PowerFortunes.com also invites like minded people, with an interest in astrology/spirituality, to join them, as Wholesale Distributors of their exclusive astrological products. A Distributor will be in-charge of marketing and selling our exclusive products directly to customers and appointing further Retail Sub-Dealers, through attractive discount schemes. Ratings PowerFortunes.com has undergone appraisal and obtained certification from several leading independent certification and inspecting agencies, so that you can be sure of hassle free, professional services, every time you avail of their services. Privacy & Confidentiality Confidentiality and safeguarding sensitive information are top on the list of priorities at PowerFortunes.com. The Site administrators follow a strict and comprehensive privacy policy, which ensures a safe and satisfying browsing experience. Location Power Fortunes is located in the foothills of the Himalayas, in Northern India.
